{"tid":1177361,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"正！歐霸決賽又比年青人一個上樓機會","createTime":"2019-05-29T18:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T15:35:59.000Z","uid":215570,"like":328,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"9abd19bc2112a2a1d36ed13bcd3c761ba89ed77a","tid":1177361,"uid":215570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T18:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVOjP5b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVOjP5b.png&h=7c7a7719&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歐霸盃又名艾瑪利盃 戰術上肯定食撚住架廢車個煙剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n架廢車仲要近10場贏得三四場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  場撚場都和 一係輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要連獌都贏唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n卡迪夫城作客都炒獌兩粒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲學人讓波 讓你老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇返阿仙奴  近幾場fit撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n踢4場波入11粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戰術上同戰績都贏撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當架廢車運氣好 唔輸 和波都贏半格 仲抵玩過21點同百家樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n好彩今日銀行批得快比我按左層樓all in阿妓 <br />\n完場打跛自己隻腳唔洗做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好同我講咩如果車贏點算  呢個世界無咁多如果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n車都贏到 我比沙利搵煙頭辣屎眼都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f437e5f92d92849cc53d966252bc226b504199","tid":1177361,"uid":64095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T18:18:30.000Z","msg":"又燈我廠"},{"pid":"7607b58003fc89c21379b26fa04a0986f14cc2d8","tid":1177361,"uid":3962,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T18:19:16.000Z","msg":"點解車仔會咁熱明明廢到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愛蛇仲要攞過咁多次"},{"pid":"bbdfe38328ade9d03bd142d5608306682fdd0b07","tid":1177361,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T18:19:29.000Z","msg":"All in 阿記"},{"pid":"c03002622f533cdeb5e0bd12d588f693051e70ab","tid":1177361,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T18:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba51e786b96a8a4bde4f453bc0108476d575d0fe","tid":1177361,"uid":55533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T18:23:41.000Z","msg":"愛sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f17c4ad7c5e1399fb9fc81719e110c48605d82c","tid":1177361,"uid":215570,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T18:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2R1NeB2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2R1NeB2.png&h=00bd46d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HWWxqJJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHWWxqJJ.png&h=c852dd07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MmhkzB3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMmhkzB3.png&h=d059e088&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k0QusW4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk